Image:Tribolium castaneum.jpg|''Tribolium castaneum''
Image:Tribolium.confusum.jpg|''Tribolium confusum'' (Tribolium brun de la farine)
Image:Oryzaephilus.surinamensis.jpg|''Oryzaephilus surinamensis'' (Sylvain)
